– `Qs5d` offsuit performs ≈ 45 % equity heads-up against a random SB range; playable but far from premium.  
– Position last-to-act post-flop (we are BB) gives us informational leverage if called.

Let’s avoid bloating with a dominated queen, yet deny easy equity to hands like small pairs and suited connectors.  
Target: einen cheap flop or fold equity now.
